      <title>Couche-Tard 未放弃收购 7-Eleven 所有者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/couche-tard-not-giving-up-on-bid-to-acquire-7-eleven-s-owner</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大便利店和燃料零售商 Alimentation Couche-Tard Inc. 仍然致力于收购其日本竞争对手 Seven &amp; i Holdings Co.，尽管提出了价值约 580 亿美元的新管理层收购提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/couche-tard-not-giving-up-on-bid-to-acquire-7-eleven-s-owner</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 13:59:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Angelini Pharma 据称将与 CVC 的 Recordati 讨论合并事宜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/angelini-pharma-said-to-discuss-combination-with-cvc-s-recordati</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，意大利制药商 Angelini Pharma SpA 正在与国内同行 Recordati SpA 就潜在合并进行谈判，后者由私募股权公司 CVC Capital Partners Plc 所有。]]></description>
