      <title>Equinor 称严冬将使亚洲和欧盟争夺天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/equinor-says-harsh-winter-would-see-asia-eu-battling-for-gas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Equinor ASA 表示，严酷的冬季将使亚洲和欧洲的消费者陷入对同一种天然气的竞争，因为燃料供应将变得紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/equinor-says-harsh-winter-would-see-asia-eu-battling-for-gas</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 13:36:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
